}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The FCC ID of this card is assumed to be MU7FPCWL04.
It would appear to have been used in some LifeBook E-series notebooks (w/ a possible code name of ''Quilt3''). :The FCC block diagram shows the CPU as a Pentium III 700/300 ULV w/ a i440MX (''Banister'') chipset.
This device has a built-in modem. :FCC Reg. No: US: EJECN00B8734
